d to institution-specific data\n\nThe good news: HistoryOfThought's encryption logic is sound (PBKDF2 600k, AES-GCM), but it's undermined by salt-in-localStorage and weak passphrases. Recommend fixing those three issues first, then adding input validation across the codebase before any LMS integration ships.\n",
